rence, Michael Fassbender, Phạm Băng Băng… tạo nên những cảnh quay vô đẹp mắt và ấn tượng.</p>","tmdb_id":127585,"cast":["Hugh Jackman","James McAvoy","Michael Fassbender","Patrick Stewart","Ian McKellen","Jennifer Lawrence","Halle Berry","Nicholas Hoult","Anna Paquin","Elliot Page","Peter Dinklage","Shawn Ashmore","Omar Sy","Evan Peters","Josh Helman"],"director":["Bryan Singer"],"keywords":["1970s","superhero","mutant","time travel","based on comic","superhuman","storm","political intrigue ","extinction","beast","claws","aftercreditsstinger","duringcreditsstinger","changing the past or future","dramatic"],"tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"127585","season":null,"vote_average":7.529,"vote_count":16009},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Hugh Jackman","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Hugh Jackman","tmdb_id":6968,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oX6CpXmnXCHLyqsa4NEed1DZAKx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/6968"},{"name":"James McAvoy","name_vi":null,"name_original":"James McAvoy","tmdb_id":5530,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/u4REKbm3zhFI2J5tVyqRovGRYUJ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/5530"},{"name":"Michael Fassbender","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Michael Fassbender","tmdb_id":17288,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xvbnUiB2ZBR3QIt595OzNy657Vw.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/17288"},{"name":"Patrick Stewart","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Patrick Stewart","tmdb_id":2387,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ufqtnLh3JJjPbEgxEag3MM5nZyv.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2387"},{"name":"Ian McKellen","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ian McKellen","tmdb_id":1327,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/coWjgMEYJjk2OrNddlXCBm8EIr3.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1327"},{"name":"Jennifer Lawrence","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jennifer Lawrence","tmdb_id":72129,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mDKMsjOMytyBiy7MHNZTa7gp7wj.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.